body:
I came across this as well. It has nothing to do with users being dumb. This is simply a bug in Devise.

@josevalim - you can reproduce the error as mentioned in the SO question.

Appropriate behaviour would be as suggested: _if the user is already signed out, then bypass the usual code and make it seem as though the user is now signed out_. Additionally, you can default to the same flash message string, "Signed out successfully.", but via `en: devise: sessions: signed_out_already:` in `en.yml` - so that we can override it if we so desire.
